@JoeUX This isn't quite how MSI works.  It will take two upgrades for you to see the fix.  One installs the fix, the problem still exists because it was in the old MSI.  Then, the problem is gone in the next MSI.  

@iSazonov The icons being removed is definitely not fixed in #12792.  The issue still existed there.
